    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "POLICE CONSTABLE Donald Cameron made out a report",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "last night and hoped the Chief Constable would believe",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "that he really DID see six flying saucers.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Pc Cameron was at home on sick leave when he looked out",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "a window and saw six glowing objects hovering in the distance.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "\"I thought I was seeing things and called my wife,\" he said last night.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "\"We watched them for about 30 seconds before they disappeared at speed",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "towards Manchester.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "\"They were about a mile",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "away. I could see them",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "clearly even though it was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "a dull day. They were white",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "and glowing.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "\"One was bigger than",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "the others with a cup-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "shaped dome - obviously",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "the mother ship. The",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "others were oval,\" he added.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "As he made out his re-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "port at his home in Chil-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
